parameters:
Originally, this school was built to study the essence of sorcery,
magic.

The chairman, who is your father, made a significant contribution to
the establishment.
This way leads to the principal's office.
[Anastasia] Actually, I have a favor to ask.
[Principal] Oh, please feel free to tell me anything.

[Principal] If it's for the students, I will assist you in any way I
can.

[Anastasia] I was a little uneasy about the items being sold in town,
so
[Anastasia] I would like to use the items being handled at the academy.

[Principal] Are you saying that there are sorcerers involved in this
disappearance case?!

[Anastasia] Just in case, I thought it would be best to prepare
thoroughly.

[Anastasia] If I remember correctly, at the academy, we were able to
alchemize valuable items that couldn't be obtained in town.
[Anastasia] I will pay for it, so I would like to use it.

[Principal] I cannot do it for free, but if you are willing to pay the
fee, I will spare no effort in assisting you.

[Principal] I can offer you a discount, but... it is a valuable item,
so

[Anastasia] I have brought a considerable amount of money with me as
well, so

[Anastasia] However, if there is still a shortage, please contact my
father in the capital.

[Anastasia] I was wondering if you could color it and give it back to
me.
[Principal] Oh, are you not going to buy anything?
[Anastasia] If I have just one of these, it will be enough.
[Principal] I have made you spend quite a bit of your money, but

[Principal] Until the student is found, the academy will support you in
all aspects of your life, so please rest assured.

[Anastasia] In case of emergency, the necessary funds will be sent from
the capital, so please don't worry.

[Anastasia] (Well... I've made the minimum preparations, so let's go
back to the forest earlier.)
